# 1. Clone the gpiozero repo somewhere on your Windows machine:
git clone https://github.com/gpiozero/gpiozero.git C:/ExtraPythonLibs/gpiozero
git clone https://github.com/raspberrypi/picamera2.git C:/ExtraPythonLibs/picamera2

# 2. In VS Code (or your editor), add that path to “python.analysis.extraPaths”:
#    (in .vscode/settings.json)
{
  "python.analysis.extraPaths": [
    "C:/ExtraPythonLibs/gpiozero",
    "C:/ExtraPythonLibs/picamera2",
  ]
}
